> ask Percy about Percy

> ask Percy about Percy
"Oy, Percy, how ya holdin' up in there?"

Percy brushes his whiskers nervously. "Well, all things considered. But I fear it won't stay that way for long, if, indeed, those mafiosos intend to put me in the ratting arena with some terrier or, worse, a ferret!"

"Don't worry, Percy," you say. "I'll bust ya out of there 'afore it comes ta that. Ya can count on your ol' pal Lil' Ragamuffin!"

Percy smiles weakly. "Yes. I know I can. God speed, Rags."
