"You, Rags? And how do you plan to defeat Jocko the fighting ferret of the Carpathians? He's renowned as the most vicious fighter to ever grace the Baleful Backwash's ratting pit! You do know that he's only lost once, right? And supposedly that was only because he was distracted by a jingling sound, as is the way of his kind."

"Then I'll make a jinglin' sound when I fight him! An' distract him!"

