> ask patron about intestines

> ask patron about intestines
"How 'bout you order some stuffed cow intestines?" you say. "That sounds like the sort of posh rubbish a great pink ox like you would like?"

"Hmmm." The gentleman patron strokes his chin until his blubbery jowels jiggle. "That sounds a right lark. Yes, I shall! Thank you, small child!"

He snaps his fingers to attract the waiter's attention. "Garcon! Garcon! I should like to order the stuffed cow intestines."

The waiter bows deeply. "Very good, monsieur."  He disappears into the kitchen, but reappears shortly carrying a steaming platter of sizzling coiled cow intestines, which he deposits onto the table in front of the pink-faced gentleman patron.
