> put record on victrola

> put record on victrola
You place the victrola on the floor, pop the Berliner gramophone record on the spindle and crank the machine to life.  A garbled but still patriotic military march spews forth from the machine's trumpet.

Murray the bum's eyes bulge and he jumps to his feet, dropping his bottle of rotgut to the floor.  His eyes are glazed, locked in a 1000 yard stare, as if his mind has been transported far away to some distant memory...

"Ten hut! About face! Private first class Murray the bum reporting for duty, sir!!" shouts Murray the bum, slapping his forehead in a crisp military salute.  "Ready to go over the trench, sir! We'll show those jerries, what for! Army strong!"

Still in a fugue, Murray the bum frog marches his way out of the room and away down the hall, shouting canned army slogans the whole way.
