The shop's interior decorator obviously suffers from an advanced case of horror vacui; every last surface in the room is covered with cheap trinkets and geegaws, and the room is a cluttered room jumble of bins and barrels, stuffed full of exotic herbs.  An overwhelming, choking stench of mothballs fills the air.

