You are at a ratting pit.
You can see The Hungarian, a ferret, a chalkboard, a poster, a golden file and a barker.
You can go north.
A gaggle of men crowd around a central pit, shouting and puffing nervously on cigarettes and waving handfuls of cash. If you squeeze through the crowd, you can see that the pit is filled with dozens of dead rats... and a single ferret hissing and squawking.
> talk to Hungarian

> talk to Hungarian
"Oy, pal, wot's all this?" you ask.  "Do not bother me, little girl," says The Hungarian, clearly distracted by the action in the pit. "Jocko is on roll. The Hungarian is set to win many pengő! So unless you are here to challenge Jocko, I have no time for you!"
> challenge Jocko

> challenge Jocko
"Oy! Fatty!" you shout, stabbing your finger into the barker's chest. "Lemme in th' pit! I'll fight  I'll take on that ferret an' I'll wipe th' walls with 'im!"

"Alright, kid, jump right in. Good luck... you'll need it!"

You hop into the pit and brace yourself.  Jocko runs at you, squeaking viciously, but you pull the jingleball from your newsie cap and toss it across the room.  Jocko skids to a halt, spins around, leaps out of the pit and chases after the ball. The assembled men hiss and boo as soon as they realize that the champ has forefeited the match, but Jocko disappears amongst the hubbub, intent only on his jingleball.

"Well, well, well, looks like we finally have a new winner! Who would have ever thought! Congrats, kid! You're taking home the golden file for all your trouble!"  He holds out the golden file.

"Darn skippy!" You grab and shove it under your newsie cap.

"Well, that's it for today's matches," announces the barker. "Since Jocko ran off, I guess we'll have to postpone any more bouts til someone catches him again."

"Is no fair! Is robbery! Cheat! Swindle!" shouts The Hungarian angrily but no one pays him much mind as the dejected gambler file out.
> x file

> x file
A golden file, the prize awarded to anyone who can beat Jocko in the ring.  It's extremely coveted by gangsters, seeing as it's exactly the perfect dimensions to be baked into a cake and delivered to an incarcerated love one. Though, to you, it appears to be a normal planeworker's file painted gold.
